<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4964430>
    dc:description "FIGURES 3–10. Dorsal view of Petalops spp. 3, P. azureus (Burmeister) (female). 4, P. bellator Brailovsky (male). 5, P. lautus sp. nov. (female). 6, P. necopinus sp. nov. (male). 7, P. occulta Brailovsky (female). 8, P. thoracicus Montandon (male). 9, P. ambiguus Brailovsky (female). 10, P. distinguendus Breddin (female)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4964430/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4964434>
    dc:description "FIGURES 11–18. Dorsal view of Petalops spp. 11, P. distinctus Montandon (male). 12, P. fortunatus Dallas (male). 13, P. graziaea sp. nov. (female). 14, P. jactatus sp. nov. (female). 15, P. luteomaculosus Brailovsky (male). 16, P. napoensis Brailovsky (male). 17, P. proletarius Breddin (male). 18, P. virago Breddin (male)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4964434/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4964426>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1–2. Metathorax view of Petalops spp. 1, P. napoensis Brailovsky (male). 2, P. distinguendus Breddin (female)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4964426/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

